            |  Why Beard Shine?
          p.lead
            | It's rather a long story, but the short version is we were tired of paying high prices for high quality beard oil. We even tried one of those "beard clubs" until we realized what was in their products. Our goal is to make an organic, great smelling beard oil — all while keeping your cost low.
