        .about-box.question-box
          h4
            span Q:
            |  When will I get my order?
          p.lead
            | We will notify you when your order ships and you'll recieve a tracking number. Since we're a small team, we only ship 3 days a week, so expect 1-2 days of handling and then 2-3 days to recieve your order. If you have any other questions, just send us an 
            a(href='mailto:beardshineatl@gmail.com') email
            | .
