        .about-box.question-box
          h4
            span Q:
            |  What's in your oil?
          p.lead
            | All of our oils start with a blend of 100% organic Jojoba & Sweet Almond Oils, both of which are proven to keep your beard healthy while protecting and nourishing the skin underneath. Also, our oil is never tested on animals and is only tested on bearded men, although many of them might look like animals.
      .col-md-6
        .about-box.question-box
          h4
            span Q:
            |  Problem with your order?
          p.lead
            | First of all, we're sorry to hear that. Secondly, please email us at 
            a(href='mailto:beardshineatl@gmail.com') beardshine@gmail.com 
            |  and we'll get back to you as soon as possible (usually in less than a day).
      .col-md-6
        .about-box.question-box
          h4
            span Q:
            |  What can I do with your oil?
          p.lead
            | Ok, you're an adult, you know what this is for. Please don't dump it in your eye or eat it. This is for external use on your beard and hair only. We are not responsible in the event of misuse.
      .col-md-6
        .about-box.question-box
          h4
            span Q:
            |  I might be allergic.
          p.lead
            | For the record, that's a statement and not a question. However, if you're not sure if our product will work for you, please email us at 
            a(href='mailto:beardshineatl@gmail.com') beardshine@gmail.com
            | , and we'll help in any way we can.
      .col-md-6
        .about-box.question-box
